  <brief_title>Observational Study on Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Retrospective-prospective Observational Study to Evaluate the Effect of Anti-viral Treatment on the Long-term Outcome in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B (SEARCH-B Study)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
